<FIRST>u i AM-Soviet-Unrest     12-01 0423</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Soviet-Unrest,0434</SECOND>
<HEAD>Leadership Calls for Calm, Death Toll Rises</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
